            "title": "Don't Wait! Prescriptions Issued within 24-48hrs",
            "des": "<p>After your consultation, our doctors can issue prescriptions for smoking cessation medications when clinically appropriate. You'll receive your prescription quickly so you can start your quit journey without delay.</p><p>We work with leading pharmacies across Australia to ensure you have convenient access to your medications. Our team will guide you through the entire process, from consultation to prescription pickup.</p><p>Medications may include nicotine replacement therapy, prescription treatments, and other evidence-based options tailored to your specific needs and medical history.</p>",
