          "type": "html",
          "settings": {
            "code": "<div style=\"text-align: center; padding: 60px 20px;\">\n  <h2 style=\"font-size: 48px; margin-bottom: 20px; color: #1a1a1a;\">We're Here to Help</h2>\n  <p style=\"font-size: 20px; color: #666; margin-bottom: 15px; max-width: 700px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\">Take the first step toward a smoke-free life. Our team of expert doctors is ready to support you on your journey to better health.</p>\n  <p style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #666; margin-bottom: 30px;\">Every quit journey is unique. Let us help you find the right path forward.</p>\n  \n  <div style=\"margin-bottom: 30px;\">\n    <a href=\"/pages/contact\" class=\"btn-theme\" style=\"display: inline-block; padding: 18px 40px; background: #ad2c34; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold; margin: 10px;\">Schedule a Consultation</a>\n  </div>\n  \n  <div style=\"margin-top: 40px; padding-top: 30px; border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0;\">\n    <p style=\"color: #666; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 16px;\"><strong>Need more information?</strong></p>\n    <p style=\"color: #666; margin-bottom: 8px;\">📧 Email: <a href=\"mailto:support@quity.com.au\" style=\"color: #ad2c34;\">support@quity.com.au</a></p>\n    <p style=\"color: #666; margin-bottom: 8px;\">📞 Phone: <a href=\"tel:1300QUITY\" style=\"color: #ad2c34;\">1300 QUITY</a></p>\n    <p style=\"color: #666; margin-top: 20px;\">\n      <a href=\"/pages/faq\" style=\"color: #ad2c34; margin: 0 15px;\">Frequently Asked Questions</a> | \n      <a href=\"/pages/how-it-works\" style=\"color: #ad2c34; margin: 0 15px;\">How It Works</a> | \n      <a href=\"/pages/contact\" style=\"color: #ad2c34; margin: 0 15px;\">Contact Us</a>\n    </p>\n  </div>\n</div>",
